{"tid":2283041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓推AI新聞女主播　","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:27:21.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ec2719a4ac0d7f1b089f6674917efe6b278c4c","tid":2283041,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，當地時間11月6日，韓國MBN電視台推出韓國首位AI主播，並順利播報了當天的主要新聞和若干條快訊。許多網友看完新聞後感慨，&ldquo;能以假亂真了&rdquo;&ldquo;厲害了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據介紹，這位AI女主播億該電視台主持人金柱夏為原型，名字同樣取&ldquo;金柱夏&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nMBN電視台，使用AI主播播報新聞，可以在發生災難等緊急情況時，迅速向觀眾播報新聞內容，而且可以一天24小時持續工作。可以節省大量人力、時間和費用成本，用來嘗試製作新的節目，可以有效節約資源。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;金柱夏&rdquo;是如何誕生的呢？據了解，&ldquo;她&rdquo;是由MBN電視台和人工智能開發公司&ldquo;MoneyBrain&rdquo;共同研發。其在對金柱夏實際主持的《綜合新聞》視頻進行10小時錄製，並對金柱夏的動作、聲音和播報過程進行長時間深度學習後誕生的產物，最多可以在一分鐘內快速生成1000字文本的播報視頻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8rlkCirmuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE8rlkCirmuM&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=c93ac3ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8rlkCirmuM</a>"},{"pid":"c7af829f65768576314a3121ae50b35e7ee1fba7","tid":2283041,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"反正韓國女人個樣都係假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/7PrkIrWIyufeZJtBvBhEraRc9PvRcGsWuQQu122L9yT0TxFXjfASYg1R9qAUhZrwA3WuSb3J_v98AUhW9VzV4GcsBgDL7vOZOXy8BYZUcHbr8jYL1gSzxw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F7PrkIrWIyufeZJtBvBhEraRc9PvRcGsWuQQu122L9yT0TxFXjfASYg1R9qAUhZrwA3WuSb3J_v98AUhW9VzV4GcsBgDL7vOZOXy8BYZUcHbr8jYL1gSzxw&h=114d60a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98977089e6f36aa543b268a3187906b1b30a06b0","tid":2283041,"uid":275498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"超,   香港都有啦<br />\n<br />\n我地有支那製 AI  錄音機做狗官"},{"pid":"64ef838627f9d3347eab4ce14910e7b17f252b24","tid":2283041,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"遲啲應該有得整做唔著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c176ea8e7c53e7ae5c8701886f45c3350797a88","tid":2283041,"uid":26618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"日本18年開始用AI主播。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/29870-2018-04-02-05-00-10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Fscienceatechnology%2F29870-2018-04-02-05-00-10.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=eaa7f2fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/29870-2018-04-02-05-00-10.html</a>"}]}